<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/angela-rayner> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Angela Rayner was Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government and Deputy Prime Minister from 5 July 2024 to 5 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Ashton-under-Lyne in May 2015."@en .
